{"type": "article", "id": 4997, "title": "混凝土蜡烛", "description": "", "date": "2015-01-07T07:25:43Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 3, "praise_count": 12, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605233552sWL0xzPTYvRrDd7j.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;\">\r\n\t来自纽约布鲁克林的建筑设计公司 IN.SEK 日前发布了一款特别的蜡烛产品，为传统的豆蜡材质裹了一个混凝土材质的外壳，并配置了一款环保木质匣子。设计团队认为，当内部的蜡烛燃尽后，用混凝土做成的容易仍然能够保留作为种植盆栽可用，寓意重生。定价 35－45 美元（约合人民币 217－279 元）不等，<a href=\"https://www.etsy.com/shop/INSEKDESIGN?section_id=15587661&amp;ref=shopsection_leftnav_9\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里尝试购买</a>。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233550b72cVFXdaSmH3fj8.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.7015625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233550M2cQp5fYvraiSByD.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6859375\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233551xJ8fw5oNhv0Rj1Ml.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.7046875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233551P56YJ3MkSRgG7qar.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.771875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233551sxDMOkf8mwGlNqni.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.2515625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;\">\r\n\t<br>\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</div>\n\n\n"}